1) NEVER SHARE YOUR PERSONAL INFO ONLINE TO ANYONE, EVER. (This includes
your real world name, address, phone #, etc. Sharing what language you speak,
what country you are from, and/or what's your hair's color is perfectly fine.)
2) Don't abuse the service. (This includes hacking, spamming, bots... and more!)
3) Be respectful and welcoming to Yoom users.
4) Don't talk about sensitive or controversial topics. That's not what Yoom is for!
5) Don't discriminate other users because of age, sex/sexuality, race and etc.
6) Do NOT cyberbully, and don't be a bystander! Report it to a moderator or a
Scratch Team member right away!
7) All message boards/chatrooms/DMs are moderated and word-filtered. If we
detect multiple attempts of swearing, attempted bypassing of filtering, and/or
spamming, this will result in a ban!
8) Posting links to websites that ARE NOT in Yoom's approved pages list or
advertising other projects without a Yoom moderator's permission is NOT
allowed, and will result in your account being restricted or put on-watch.
9) Try to keep messages sweet and short, we don't have that much server space!
(We literally have 756 bytes to use at a time, please don't break something this good)
10) Don't be a stranger, make friends, and have fun!
